The board shall, through the promulgation of administrative regulations, set appropriate fees and penalties for:
The application process;
Verification of qualifications;
Issuance and renewal of licenses for advanced imaging professionals, medical imaging technologists, radiographers, radiation therapists, nuclear medicine technologists, and limited X-ray machine operators;
Duplicate licenses;
Home study courses for limited X-ray machine operators;
Late renewals or reinstatements;
Violations;
Checks issued on accounts with insufficient funds; and
Any other actions as deemed appropriate by the board.
